metadata.name: AQUA.PVNP
metadata.description: AQUA.PVNP was created by Nicola Formichetti, DRESSX and Alejandro Delgado in conjunction with Pabllo Vittar's new live album ‘I Am Pabllo’. All the NFTs from the drop are wearable in augmented reality and will be available for the owners on the DRESSX app.
